1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

2
00:00:03,900 --> 00:00:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Haneda?</font>

3
00:00:05,210 --> 00:00:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay to have just one 
graduation ceremony for Isaki?</font>

4
00:00:09,660 --> 00:00:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most people only ever get one.</font>

5
00:00:12,380 --> 00:00:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We heard about it from Isaki.</font>

6
00:00:14,470 --> 00:00:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once she graduates, 
she's going to become two people.</font>

7
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But until the two of them turn human, 
they can't both exist at the same time.</font>

8
00:00:23,450 --> 00:00:26,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it. That's what you mean.</font>

9
00:00:26,510 --> 00:00:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Isaki's only chance, 
so we should hold two graduations for her!</font>

10
00:00:31,070 --> 00:00:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next full moon's four days from now!</font>

11
00:00:33,190 --> 00:00:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'll be the last chance 
for us to meet the other Isaki.</font>

12
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The school's real graduation ceremony 
isn't for another week.</font>

13
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we hold our own ceremony 
on the full moon in four days?</font>

14
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. I think that's a great idea.</font>

15
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It almost reminds me of a wedding!</font>

16
00:00:53,530 --> 00:00:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kind with two ceremonies! How lovely!</font>

17
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Rei, what kind of 
wedding would you prefer?</font>

18
00:01:00,910 --> 00:01:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-We're talking 
about graduations right now!</font>

19
00:01:03,810 --> 00:01:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get back on topic and think 
about what to do for Isaki's graduation!</font>

20
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While we're at it, why 
don't we make it a surprise?</font>

21
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like it! I'm all for a good surprise!</font>

22
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She won't know what's coming to her!</font>

23
00:01:17,700 --> 00:01:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's that, then!</font>

24
00:01:19,290 --> 00:01:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's keep it a secret 
from her until then!</font>

25
00:01:25,130 --> 00:01:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

26
00:01:26,870 --> 00:01:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Everyone's here early today.</font>

27
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14"><font color="#5a5b58">Mathematics</font></font></font></font>

28
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm studying for my entrance exams.</font>

29
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bowledoodle's so cute!</font>

30
00:01:38,190 --> 00:01:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Rei! I love, love, love you!</font>

31
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="13"><font color="#effefb">The Misanthrope and the Comet's Pilgrimage</font></font></font></font>

32
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="13"><font color="#effefb">The Misanthrope and the Comet's Pilgrimage</font></font></font></font>

33
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#f5f5f5">Episode <font size="21">10</font></font></font></font></font>

34
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#f5f5f5">Episode <font size="21">10</font></font></font></font></font>

35
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A surprise graduation ceremony, huh?</font>

36
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If it's in the classroom, 
she might find out while we set up.</font>

37
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the biggest issue here.</font>

38
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to find somewhere 
that Isaki wouldn't go.</font>

39
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about the empty 
classroom next to the library?</font>

40
00:03:30,860 --> 00:03:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She might find out 
when she goes to the library.</font>

41
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the conference room?</font>

42
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too close to the teachers' office.</font>

43
00:03:38,370 --> 00:03:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't be too rowdy 
with the other teachers nearby.</font>

44
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where should it be, then?</font>

45
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about the A/V room?</font>

46
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea!</font>

47
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's soundproof, and we 
can use the projector!</font>

48
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds good to me!</font>

49
00:03:54,390 --> 00:03:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think so, too.</font>

50
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sounds like our best choice.</font>

51
00:03:58,620 --> 00:04:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

52
00:04:00,450 --> 00:04:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like the idea, too.</font>

53
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll find out if we can use 
the A/V room that day.</font>

54
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Mr. Hitoma!</font>

55
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:12,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kinda ceremony will it be for Ichaki?</font>

56
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I propose that we make it a fun one!</font>

57
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A serious ceremony will emphasize 
what a big milestone it is.</font>

58
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They both have their charms, don't they?</font>

59
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I like the do-it-yourself feel this has.</i></font>

60
00:04:27,850 --> 00:04:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have to do all I can to make it 
a good graduation ceremony.</i></font>

61
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#7b8184"><font size="30">Advanced Class</font></font></b></font>

62
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

63
00:04:38,090 --> 00:04:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like everyone's been 
acting distant to me lately.</font>

64
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

65
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention they all run 
off somewhere after school.</font>

66
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't think that's true.</font>

67
00:04:51,130 --> 00:04:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have much time left 
to spend with them.</font>

68
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now they're all treating me 
differently than before.</font>

69
00:05:00,650 --> 00:05:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help but feel 
like they're avoiding me...</font>

70
00:05:07,020 --> 00:05:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ohgami, do you mind if I share 
how you feel with the others?</font>

71
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

72
00:05:13,460 --> 00:05:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

73
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they really <i>are</i> avoiding me, 
I don't think I could ever recover.</font>

74
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can guarantee that's not the case.</font>

75
00:05:22,850 --> 00:05:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

76
00:05:24,110 --> 00:05:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry!</font>

77
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:27,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's definitely not what's going on!</font>

78
00:05:28,290 --> 00:05:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really?</font>

79
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! Yep! Uh-huh!</font>

80
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you say so...</font>

81
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then sure, go ahead.</font>

82
00:05:36,810 --> 00:05:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Ohgami!</font>

83
00:05:38,970 --> 00:05:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just wait right here!</font>

84
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you all right, Mr. Hitoma?!</font>

85
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Di... Di... Di...</font>

86
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die?! Please don't die on me!</font>

87
00:05:57,710 --> 00:06:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No... Directly to the A/V room...</font>

88
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

89
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#656c6f"><font size="22">A/V Room</font></font></b></font>

90
00:06:08,090 --> 00:06:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I go inside?</font>

91
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

92
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I go...</font>

93
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me...</font>

94
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on graduating!</font>

95
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're sorry we made you worry!</font>

96
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

97
00:06:24,100 --> 00:06:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're sorry.</font>

98
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how tomorrow's the full moon?</font>

99
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we were planning on holding 
a graduation ceremony for the other Isaki.</font>

100
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was meant to be a surprise, 
but not if it ends up worrying you. Isaki.</font>

101
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We want to congratulate both Isakis!</font>

102
00:06:43,250 --> 00:06:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

103
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, it looks amazing!</font>

104
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You prepared all of this?</font>

105
00:06:52,170 --> 00:06:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

106
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did our best to make it look cute!</font>

107
00:06:57,580 --> 00:06:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine, I guess.</font>

108
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami says that, 
but she got pretty into it, too.</font>

109
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was like, "I hope Isaki likes it!"</font>

110
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to tell her that!</font>

111
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone... I'm so glad...</font>

112
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was worried that you 
were all avoiding me...</font>

113
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone here is happy for you, Ohgami.</font>

114
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Thank you so much!</font>

115
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, all we're doing is having 
the graduation ceremony tomorrow.</font>

116
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That may be so...</font>

117
00:07:31,210 --> 00:07:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I also thought it'd be nice 
to let Isaki celebrate her graduation.</font>

118
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:41,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm happy to see that
you all care so much about Isaki.</font>

119
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get the wrong idea.</font>

120
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just for Isaki tomorrow.</font>

121
00:07:48,420 --> 00:07:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We care about the Isaki here, too.</font>

122
00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

123
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget about that!</font>

124
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To tell you the truth, 
I was jealous of you and Isaki.</font>

125
00:07:59,110 --> 00:08:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You both value and care 
equally as much for each other.</font>

126
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope the two of you find 
wonderful things in your futures!</font>

127
00:08:09,770 --> 00:08:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone... Thank you so much!</font>

128
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ee8286"><b><font size="30">Happy <font color="#f1b577">Graduation <font color="#f190c2">Isaki</font></font></font></b></font></font>

129
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff"><b><font size="30"><font face="Times New Roman">The Next Day</font></font></b></font></font>

130
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will hereby award the diploma.</font>

131
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#050201">Diploma of Graduation
<font size="17">Isaki Ohgami
<font size="14">This certifies that the above individual has completed all of the prescribed studies.
 Shiranui Private High School
<font size="12">Principal <font size="17">Shiro Karasuma</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

132
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Graduating student, Isaki Ohgami.</font>

133
00:08:27,070 --> 00:08:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

134
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki. Congratulations on graduating.</font>

135
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Tobari.</font>

136
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that you'll do just fine 
in the human world, Isaki.</font>

137
00:08:43,130 --> 00:08:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have my word.</font>

138
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you lead a wonderful life 
without any regrets.</font>

139
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

140
00:08:50,350 --> 00:08:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go grab some tasty desserts someday 
when we're both human!</font>

141
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! One day for sure!</font>

142
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:07,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, everyone!</font>

143
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b>3 Days Later</b></font></font>

144
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We will hereby award the diploma.</font>

145
00:09:15,650 --> 00:09:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Graduating student, Isaki Ohgami.</font>

146
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes!</font>

147
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki Ohgami.</font>

148
00:09:27,050 --> 00:09:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations to you!</font>

149
00:09:30,110 --> 00:09:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Principal!</font>

150
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your graduation is the culmination 
of your hard-earned efforts.</font>

151
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing can change that fact.</font>

152
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll always remember 
with pride having had you as a student.</font>

153
00:09:57,910 --> 00:10:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sad that Ichaki's graduating!</font>

154
00:10:01,650 --> 00:10:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, Machi!</font>

155
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help it!</font>

156
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Please don't cry, Machi...</font>

157
00:10:12,470 --> 00:10:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now <i>you're</i> crying, Isaki!</font>

158
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey now, lay off her for today.</font>

159
00:10:17,930 --> 00:10:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. Aren't you sad, too, Sui?</font>

160
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

161
00:10:23,010 --> 00:10:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

162
00:10:24,170 --> 00:10:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll feel like something's missing.</font>

163
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami...</font>

164
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be sad to miss out 
on that surly affection of yours.</font>

165
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's</i> why?!</font>

166
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma!</font>

167
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

168
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for everything 
over the past two years.</font>

169
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah.</font>

170
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Isaki within me has served 
as a beacon of hope all this time.</font>

171
00:10:56,090 --> 00:11:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gave us the chance for Isaki 
and I to come to an understanding.</font>

172
00:11:01,990 --> 00:11:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't thank you enough.</font>

173
00:11:05,190 --> 00:11:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ohgami...</font>

174
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should be thanking you.</font>

175
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ohgami, your actions and outcomes came 
from your own decisions.</font>

176
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:18,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that you two will do just fine.</font>

177
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish the two of you 
happy lives going forward.</font>

178
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma.</font>

179
00:11:27,590 --> 00:11:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

180
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wish is the same!</font>

181
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too!</font>

182
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:37,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you all so much!</font>

183
00:11:38,210 --> 00:11:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations once again!</font>

184
00:11:39,650 --> 00:11:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congrats!</font>

185
00:11:40,930 --> 00:11:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#656c6f"><font size="18">Conference Room</font></font></b></font>

186
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go!</font>

187
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers, everyone!</font>

188
00:11:46,310 --> 00:11:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

189
00:11:50,530 --> 00:11:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, human.</font>

190
00:11:53,170 --> 00:11:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not drinking much, are we?</font>

191
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, let me top you off.</font>

192
00:12:00,170 --> 00:12:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you.</font>

193
00:12:01,890 --> 00:12:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what are <i>you</i> 
doing here, Miss Alice?!</font>

194
00:12:04,980 --> 00:12:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Figured I'd celebrate 
the occasion by sneaking in.</font>

195
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looked like fun.</font>

196
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that really okay?</font>

197
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's fine.</font>

198
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've cast a spell on myself so I can
only be seen by people I've met before.</font>

199
00:12:19,170 --> 00:12:21,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, who's this?</font>

200
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

201
00:12:22,570 --> 00:12:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He can see you just fine!</i></font>

202
00:12:24,850 --> 00:12:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you're...</font>

203
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Alice.</font>

204
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't get 
in a married man's face like that.</font>

205
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? He's taken?</font>

206
00:12:33,810 --> 00:12:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma, who <i>is</i> this?</font>

207
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alice! How dare you show your face here!</font>

208
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, rats.</font>

209
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, is she an acquaintance 
of the principal?</font>

210
00:12:48,010 --> 00:12:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... You could say that.</font>

211
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

212
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems a friend 
of the principal joined our party.</font>

213
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that, Satoru.</font>

214
00:12:59,250 --> 00:13:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki's already on her 
sixth bottle, you know.</font>

215
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

216
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotta start with the most expensive 
and delicious booze first...</font>

217
00:13:11,460 --> 00:13:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hoshino's got it rough...</font>

218
00:13:19,850 --> 00:13:21,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel awful...</font>

219
00:13:22,250 --> 00:13:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get to work.</font>

220
00:13:23,850 --> 00:13:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

221
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:26,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you slacking off?</font>

222
00:13:26,630 --> 00:13:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had too much to drink, 
and now I'm hungover.</font>

223
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm getting second thoughts 
about giving you this important job.</font>

224
00:13:35,490 --> 00:13:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A job?</font>

225
00:13:36,730 --> 00:13:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hitoma. I want you to be my mailman.</font>

226
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me?</font>

227
00:13:44,710 --> 00:13:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wrote this letter while 
I was doing my assignment.</font>

228
00:13:47,290 --> 00:13:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to deliver it 
to Seiko in my place.</font>

229
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would have liked to go myself, 
but I didn't manage to graduate.</font>

230
00:13:57,790 --> 00:14:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm here to ask you, Hitoma.</font>

231
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami.</font>

232
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to visit her grave.</font>

233
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">School rules forbid any unauthorized 
transmission of information off-campus.</font>

234
00:14:12,050 --> 00:14:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that!</font>

235
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured it'd be a long shot.</font>

236
00:14:16,490 --> 00:14:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

237
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay if I take this letter for now?</font>

238
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see what the principal has to say.</font>

239
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hitoma. Thanks.</font>

240
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't promise I'll deliver it to Seiko.</font>

241
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's okay.</font>

242
00:14:33,850 --> 00:14:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't, then I'll accept it.</font>

243
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no other choice.</font>

244
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'll try asking.</font>

245
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I take the bus from here?</i></font>

246
00:14:54,930 --> 00:14:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The bus stop should be...</i></font>

247
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, excuse me.</font>

248
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could I ask you something?</font>

249
00:15:05,130 --> 00:15:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

250
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assumed you were a local.</font>

251
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we just happened to have the same
destination, and I know the way there.</font>

252
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My student asked me to deliver a letter 
to the grave of her former caretaker.</font>

253
00:15:18,010 --> 00:15:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what a wonderful teacher you are.</font>

254
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I wouldn't go that far.</font>

255
00:15:24,570 --> 00:15:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure she would have 
wanted to make the trip herself.</font>

256
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A letter for her caretaker's grave?</font>

257
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an admirable girl.</font>

258
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Oh...</font>

259
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I forgot to introduce myself, 
but my name is Rei Hitoma.</font>

260
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How polite of you.</font>

261
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for me, I'm Sae Kizaki.</font>

262
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Kizaki?</font>

263
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

264
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, would your mother's name 
happen to be Seiko Kizaki?</font>

265
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

266
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know that?</font>

267
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#474d54">Kizaki Family</font></font></b></font>

268
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for waiting. Go ahead.</font>

269
00:16:15,930 --> 00:16:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon my intrusion.</font>

270
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mrs. Seiko, it's nice to meet you.</i></font>

271
00:16:21,180 --> 00:16:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm Rei Hitoma, Usami's homeroom teacher.</i></font>

272
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Usami studies and works hard every day 
with the help of her classmates.</i></font>

273
00:16:32,970 --> 00:16:38,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As her teacher, I know she's diligent,
and cares very much for those around her.</i></font>

274
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've come here today 
with a letter from Usami.</i></font>

275
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I also received a letter 
from her the other day.</i></font>

276
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was a wonderful, honest, 
and heartfelt letter.</i></font>

277
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure she's put great thought 
into writing a wonderful letter for you.</i></font>

278
00:17:00,090 --> 00:17:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm here in her place today,</i></font>

279
00:17:02,020 --> 00:17:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I know that she'll graduate 
and visit in person one day.</i></font>

280
00:17:05,470 --> 00:17:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please wait until that day comes.</i></font>

281
00:17:10,600 --> 00:17:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's all from me.</i></font>

282
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:16,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Sae, thank you 
for letting me pay a visit.</font>

283
00:17:16,950 --> 00:17:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I'm sure 
my mother's delighted.</font>

284
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cosmos...</font>

285
00:17:24,650 --> 00:17:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your student must have 
known my mother very well.</font>

286
00:17:28,870 --> 00:17:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

287
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cosmos were my mother's favorite flowers.</font>

288
00:17:33,930 --> 00:17:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their color reminded her of a stuffed 
rabbit she had ever since she was a child.</font>

289
00:17:40,630 --> 00:17:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it had gone missing.</font>

290
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I looked for it before the funeral, 
but I never found it.</font>

291
00:17:49,090 --> 00:17:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still regret not being 
able to place it in her coffin.</font>

292
00:17:57,010 --> 00:17:58,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for everything today.</font>

293
00:17:58,990 --> 00:18:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you as well.</font>

294
00:18:02,570 --> 00:18:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give my regards to your student.</font>

295
00:18:05,260 --> 00:18:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will do.</font>

296
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So long.</font>

297
00:18:11,510 --> 00:18:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

298
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stuffed rabbit!</font>

299
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, my student got it 
as a gift from Mrs. Kizaki.</font>

300
00:18:20,410 --> 00:18:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

301
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was fall two years ago.</font>

302
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My student visited her in the hospital, 
and received it then.</font>

303
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So there's no need to worry!</font>

304
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her stuffed rabbit is alive 
and well to this very day!</font>

305
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you serious?</font>

306
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Usami's doing just fine!</font>

307
00:18:40,210 --> 00:18:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief.</font>

308
00:18:43,150 --> 00:18:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami loves gossip, 
so make sure she talks a lot to her.</font>

309
00:18:49,210 --> 00:18:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'll let her know.</font>

310
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's my contact information.</font>

311
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give this to your student.</font>

312
00:18:58,580 --> 00:19:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She can reach out if she ever needs help.</font>

313
00:19:02,170 --> 00:19:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if she doesn't, 
I'd love to speak with her someday.</font>

314
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'll make it happen.</font>

315
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami?</font>

316
00:19:19,220 --> 00:19:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you deliver my letter to Seiko?</font>

317
00:19:22,390 --> 00:19:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

318
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:26,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And as luck would have it, 
I also ran into her daughter, Sae.</font>

319
00:19:26,630 --> 00:19:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got to meet Sae?!</font>

320
00:19:28,650 --> 00:19:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was she still a cheeky brat?</font>

321
00:19:31,450 --> 00:19:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly is your image of Ms. Sae?</font>

322
00:19:35,570 --> 00:19:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rotten brat who never listens.</font>

323
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What'd you two talk about?</font>

324
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She told me that Usami loves gossip, 
so you should talk a lot to her.</font>

325
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sae and Seiko are 
the ones who love to gossip.</font>

326
00:19:48,780 --> 00:19:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, I received Ms. Sae's 
contact information.</font>

327
00:19:53,890 --> 00:19:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you graduate, you can go meet her.</font>

328
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! Got it!</font>

329
00:19:58,660 --> 00:20:00,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll try even harder!</font>

330
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll graduate, and see 
how big Sae's gotten!</font>

331
00:20:04,770 --> 00:20:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

332
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I have another new goal!</font>

333
00:20:09,650 --> 00:20:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hitoma!</font>

334
00:20:10,630 --> 00:20:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for going to talk with Sae!</font>

335
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to talk to Sae, too, someday!</font>

336
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#656c6f"><font size="22">Director's Office</font></font></b></font>

337
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's begin our interview.</font>

338
00:20:23,170 --> 00:20:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was the past year for you?</font>

339
00:20:26,090 --> 00:20:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I learned even more over the last year.</font>

340
00:20:30,370 --> 00:20:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weakness can be just as necessary a trait.</font>

341
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The people around you 
will be there to help.</font>

342
00:20:36,230 --> 00:20:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That shooting stars 
in the summer are beautiful.</font>

343
00:20:39,370 --> 00:20:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How important it is to think for yourself.</font>

344
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that you should say what's 
on your mind when you can.</font>

345
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. One last question.</font>

346
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mr. Hitoma. Do you like humans?</font>

347
00:20:57,220 --> 00:20:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate humans.</font>

348
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, I think there's more 
about them I can forgive since last year.</font>

349
00:21:03,820 --> 00:21:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That's just like you.</font>

350
00:21:07,420 --> 00:21:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will there be any intermediate 
students moving up this year?</font>

351
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There sure are.</font>

352
00:21:12,430 --> 00:21:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we're getting a new teacher.</font>

353
00:21:15,210 --> 00:21:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?!</font>

354
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously.</font>

355
00:21:17,190 --> 00:21:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what they're like...</font>

356
00:21:19,630 --> 00:21:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to see the file?</font>

357
00:21:21,110 --> 00:21:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I really?!</font>

358
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all ears, huh?</font>

359
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might want to take a moment 
to prepare yourself, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

360
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This teacher will be the assistant 
homeroom teacher for the advanced class.</font>

361
00:21:35,130 --> 00:21:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you mean I'll be 
working with them a lot?</font>

362
00:21:39,210 --> 00:21:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

363
00:21:40,620 --> 00:21:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you ready?</font>

364
00:21:42,890 --> 00:21:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

365
00:21:44,130 --> 00:21:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look, then.</font>

366
00:21:48,540 --> 00:21:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="22"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#363432">Resume</font></font></font></font>

367
00:21:48,540 --> 00:21:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#363432">Furigana       Mirai Haruna</font></font></font></font>

368
00:21:48,540 --> 00:21:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#363432">Full Name      <font size="22">Mirai Haruna</font></font></font></font></font>

369
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mirai Haruna.</font>

370
00:21:58,050 --> 00:22:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll be your junior co-worker 
starting with the new term.</font>

371
00:23:32,950 --> 00:23:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial"><font color="#ebfeef"><b>Next Episode:</b></font></font></font></font>

372
00:23:32,950 --> 00:23:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="19"><font face="Arial"><font color="#ebfeef"><b>The Misanthrope and the Nigh Past</b></font></font></font></font>

